addr="jonmsterling"
title="Jon Sterling">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:parent>jms-00J2</fr:parent></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
 <fr:p>We use the fact that the additive operation of the boolean semiring is disjunction and the multiplicative operation is conjunction:</fr:p>

 <fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[   \begin {aligned}    {\mathopen {}\left (N\cdot  M\right )\mathclose {}}_{i,j} &= \bigoplus _{k\in {\mathopen {}\left  [m\right  ]\mathclose {}}} M_{i,k}\cdot  N_{k,j}    \\    &=    \bigvee _{k\in {\mathopen {}\left  [m\right  ]\mathclose {}}} M_{i,k}\land  N_{k,j}    \\    &=    \exists  k\in {\mathopen {}\left  [m\right  ]\mathclose {}}\mathpunct {.}    M_{i,k}\land  N_{k,j}   \end {aligned}  ]]></fr:tex>
</fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree>
 
