title="Jon Sterling">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Let <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[M]]></fr:tex> be an <html:span
xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
style="white-space: nowrap"><fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[{\mathopen {}\left (l\times  m\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex>-<fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00IS.xml"
addr="jms-00IS"
title="Matrix over a semiring">matrix</fr:link></html:span> and let <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[N]]></fr:tex> be a <html:span
